Spica satis pauciflora, obovoideo-ellipsoidea, 5-8 mm longa, bracteis infimis brevibus, apice subrotunda- tis, intermediis obovato-ellipticis‚ circiter 6 mm longis, om- nino ecssiatis, superne carinatis, area dorsali bene evoluta. Sepala lateralia postice alte connata, lineari-lanceolata, obtusa, apice pilis albidis v. fulvescentibus villosa, ala carinali in partibus tertiis media summaque ciliata.
